{"tid":562751,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾發表中國滲透政界研究　紐西蘭學者近日辦公室、家居被爆竊　收警告信","createTime":"2018-02-16T08:06:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-16T09:00:45.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"20c418003b6166880323372b4547fcb030db2528","tid":562751,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T08:06:41.000Z","msg":"一名曾發表論文研究中國如何在外國建立政治影響力的紐西蘭學者，周五向澳洲國會透露，近日其辦公室及家居接連被闖入爆竊，她又收到指她將受到襲擊的警告信，她在中國時訪問的消息來源亦被中國當局問話。<br />\n<br />\n紐西蘭坎特伯雷大學（University of Canterbury）教授Anne-Marie Brady，周五在澳洲國會的情報及安全委員會作證時透露，近日發生三宗令她憂慮的事件，包括去年12月其辦公室被爆竊、本周收到她將會被襲擊的警告信，而昨日其家居亦被爆竊。<br />\n<br />\n她指，家居被爆竊的事件最可疑，因為3部可攜式電腦及電話均被偷，但其他值錢的財物卻完好無缺，警方正調查事件。<br />\n<br />\nBrady又透露，自從她發報有關中國南極政策的研究後，其大學僱主亦被施壓，而她在中國訪問時的消息來源，均被中國國安問話。<br />\n<br />\nBrady去年9月刊出一份論文《魔術武器（Magic Weapons）》，以紐西蘭為案例，研究中國如何在國外施加影響力，引起國內外廣泛關注，論文提到執政黨收到大筆政治捐獻，與及一些前高官及現任高官的家屬如何獲委入中國國營銀行、企業及智庫的董事局內。<br />\n<br />\n該研究引發新西蘭優先黨提出要作出調查，而澳洲現時正引入法例遏止中國在當地政治的影響。<br />\n<br />\nBrady又提到，中國的非國家活動，正以統一陣線（united front)的名號下被協調統調，以左右公眾輿論及政治精英，去支持其冒起的新外交政策。<br />\n<br />\n「澳洲及紐西蘭似乎是近年這一策略的試驗區，而現時已去到關鍵水平。」她表示。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/%E6%9B%BE%E7%99%BC%E8%A1%A8%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%BB%B2%E9%80%8F%E6%94%BF%E7%95%8C%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6-%E7%B4%90%E8%A5%BF%E8%98%AD%E5%AD%B8%E8%80%85%E8%BF%91%E6%97%A5%E8%BE%A6%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%A4-%E5%AE%B6%E5%B1%85%E8%A2%AB%E7%88%86%E7%AB%8A-%E6%94%B6%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E4%BF%A1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%259B%25BE%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25BB%25B2%25E9%2580%258F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E7%2595%258C%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6-%25E7%25B4%2590%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E8%2598%25AD%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E8%2580%2585%25E8%25BF%2591%25E6%2597%25A5%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25AE%25A4-%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25B1%2585%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E7%2588%2586%25E7%25AB%258A-%25E6%2594%25B6%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2591%258A%25E4%25BF%25A1%2F&d=MBLLgfJYEfumY1yC02Akaf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=91b6614b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%259B%25BE%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25BB%25B2%25E9%2580%258F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E7%2595%258C%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6-%25E7%25B4%2590%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E8%2598%25AD%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E8%2580%2585%25E8%25BF%2591%25E6%2597%25A5%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25AE%25A4-%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25B1%2585%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E7%2588%2586%25E7%25AB%258A-%25E6%2594%25B6%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2591%258A%25E4%25BF%25A1%2F&h=e2c05cfe\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/international/%E6%9B%BE%E7%99%BC%E8%A1%A8%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%BB%B2%E9%80%8F%E6%94%BF%E7%95%8C%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6-%E7%B4%90%E8%A5%BF%E8%98%AD%E5%AD%B8%E8%80%85%E8%BF%91%E6%97%A5%E8%BE%A6%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%A4-%E5%AE%B6%E5%B1%85%E8%A2%AB%E7%88%86%E7%AB%8A-%E6%94%B6%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E4%BF%A1/</a>"},{"pid":"50336e802c9e7848aa872ce28682c13e412580fc","tid":562751,"uid":83582,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T08:16:02.000Z","msg":"支那果然係爛仔大國"},{"pid":"77795c2405a4e3fa7e10dbd6e6ed93dab07ed87a","tid":562751,"uid":171718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T08:16:22.000Z","msg":"此地無銀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4374fa0e335b8dc1719179b669a40e96d425061b","tid":562751,"uid":61462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T08:28:22.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"92ff5514dd6733a42c676d32cec6e8334aa04d00","tid":562751,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T08:43:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea444bdc86edec1a3e999a48182e675091d62428","tid":562751,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T09:00:45.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n直接隊冧佢算啦，洗乜出信"}]}